<br>
On average most 50 infiltrators have between +20-30 from items. While SBs have between +35-45.<br>
<br>
Just doing some rough estimation, SBs have more spec points with items that infiltrators get. I came up with around 2.8X for SBs vs 2.675 for infs.<br>
<br>
At 50 we have a total of 1 +CS item and that is +3. <br>
<br>
For envenom we have only 2 items up to 50 that is +envenom and both overlap each other considering the fact they both fit in the jewel slot.<br>
<br>
For stealth at 50, if we wear our epic armor we take a substantial hit in the +stealth items as none of our armor has +stealth to it. <br>
<br>
So what does this mean about 2.5X spec points we may get the higher styles in melee skills, but they are all horrible in pulling off (with the exception of dragonfang). <br>
<br>
We can spec higher in stealth, but there is no point because when it comes to math and Mythic 36=50.<br>
